skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: phillipine guide
des: This guide provides useful information of the top tourist destinations and attractions in the Philippines. Get the latest headlines by saying "Alexa, ask Philippine Guide for local news". Say "Alexa, open Philippine Guide" to launch the app or say "Alexa, ask Philippine Guide for an attraction".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
